---
title: Duck A L'Orange with Parsley Mash and Roasted Carrots
description: We love a good Duck A L'Orange with Mash & Carrots and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/duck-a-l-orange-d3678707-470ca64a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/duck-a-l-orange-5d7a587c8d88ef00115a6ed4-481f69ce.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
